---
// GAMES — the sims' shelf. When the lab went zero-g (V3, 2026-07-20) the
// seven experiments moved out of /lab and into this one room, as floating
// doorways. The doors keep their multiverse heritage: each plate carries
// the keeper's swatch + number from the universe that adopted it — the lab
// is where the other universes live on. Bodies are draggable (/mv/zerog.js);
// the percent homes below park them whenever physics is off.
---

<html lang="en">
